<br>
First things first, WD is kinda like splurt. All the damage comes at the end. That being said make sure you cancel magic it off you. Yes this means you need to have your top two buff slots open but I'm sure you already know that. A fairly decent strategy is to shock em when they start healing because it interupts close to %100 of the time. Between shocks hit em with your best nukes. It is a good idea to golem wand the druid before you start in on them as they have a ton of buffs and you don't want them zipping away from you.<br>
<br>
The bad news is unless you are lvl 60 if a druid decides to just take your nukes and outheal them you will be in some serious trouble. The good news is they wont be able to kill you either so it is kind of a stalemate. Go wait for that druid to finish his quad then wand him and nuke him into the ground. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uauroreakengro.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aurore Akengro</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/12/02 2:24:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=64.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grrr Druids...</span><hr size=1> The only thing I try against druids is sunstrike followed by ice spear. This has a chance of taking them out. If not, then just gate <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Aurore
